    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >***</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得的游戏币和物品可与主游戏《Paw Paw Destiny》共享。如果感兴趣，请查看捆绑套装。(如果两款游戏都有，您还可以在主游戏中玩节日游戏）</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【炼狱棋盘游戏 Purrgatorium Watcher】(board game, 4 min/ a play) </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Card * TurnBase * TowerDefence * RogueLite]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为天堂和地狱之间的炼狱法官，阻止 12 名罪人逃跑和潜入，成为该区域的守护者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027590/extras/d1cf7f83ba8ed29b369cc4f9ca444668.poster.avif?t=1757310400\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027590/extras/d1cf7f83ba8ed29b369cc4f9ca444668.webm?t=1757310400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027590/extras/d1cf7f83ba8ed29b369cc4f9ca444668.mp4?t=1757310400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【猫狗主题卡 Pawnishment Card deck】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用门票解锁各种伤害卡，你可以自由地大谈你想出的伤害方法。(1,008 张卡片）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Cosmic Pawâtissier (城市发展)】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为天界的创意糕点师，为人类提供美味奇特的文明甜点。以混乱的方式改变该地区的历史！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027590/extras/87c1f374466fad99253415c325605366.avif?t=1757310400\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【(Cat/Dog) 主角定制】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100型X多种颜色，用于无限数量的原始编辑。打扮并进行冒险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027590/extras/6169c4ef4fa0eddf1d301e0ab75235e0.avif?t=1757310400\" width=600 height=220 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
